程序包org.springframework.web.multipart的分层结构

程序包分层结构:
  • 所有程序包

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable (implements java.io.Serializable)
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • org.springframework.core.NestedRuntimeException
            • org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartException
              • org.springframework.web.multipart.MaxUploadSizeExceededException

接口分层结构

  • org.springframework.core.io.InputStreamSource
    • org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartFile
  • org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartRequest
    • org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartHttpServletRequest (并 extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest)
  • org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartResolver
  • javax.servlet.ServletRequest
    • javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest
      • org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartHttpServletRequest (并 extends org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartRequest)
